### Smart Classroom API - Authentication Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### Variables are loaded from .env file

@baseUrl = http://{{$dotenv API_HOST}}:{{$dotenv API_PORT}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv API_KEY}}

### ===========================================
### Health Check
### ===========================================

### Check server health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ===========================================
### User Registration & Login
### ===========================================

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "test0123"
}

###

### Login user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "test0123"
}
